CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.Sign on podium reads "Democrats for United Action: A Voluntary Service Organization of the Democratic Party"
TitMainTitle: Democrats for United Action rally for David L. Lawrence, with speaker at microphone, large portrait of Lawrence, and wave patterned carpeting
